comments: Beasley's (MIL) left hand comes forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Williams Jr.'s (MEM) front as Williams Jr. momentarily mishandles the ball.
Lopez (MIL) maintains a rested forearm on Williams Jr.'s (MEM) side and marginal contact occurs as Williams Jr. mishandles the ball on his own at the end of the drive.
Lopez (MIL) steps forward slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Williams Jr. (MEM) as Williams Jr. makes the pass.

Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his right arm forward to contest the shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with the side of Stevens' (MEM) head during Stevens' upward shooting motion. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Aldama (MEM) cleanly blocks Beasley's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Williams Jr. (MEM) releases his off-arm away from Beasley's (MIL) front and marginal contact occurs as Williams Jr. slows his momentum near the sideline.
Crowder (MIL) brings his left hand forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Williams' (MEM) right shoulder during the drive. Lopez (MIL) then cleanly dislodges the ball away from Williams.
Lopez (MIL) dives to the floor and makes clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental contact occurs with Williams (MEM).
Williams (MEM) dives into Lopez's (MIL) upper body, allowing him to then make contact with the ball thereafter.

Antetokounmpo (MIL) moves into Williams Jr. (MEM) and initiates body contact during the jump shot attempt. After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that the contact occurred prior to the expiration of the shot clock.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his off-arm outward prior to marginal contact occurring with Williams' (MEM) slightly extended left arm as Williams defends the drive.
Beasley (MIL) and Crowder (MIL) each bring an arm forward toward Williams Jr.'s (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs with Williams Jr.'s front as he splits the double team.
Lillard (MIL) brings his left arm forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Williams' (MEM) left arm/side.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) wraps both arms around Williams' (MEM) midsection, affecting Williams' SQBR and subsequently allowing Antetokounmpo to make contact with the ball.
Williams (MEM) is moving forward when marginal body contact occurs with Lillard (MIL) as Lillard stops his forward momentum during the inbound.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Williams Jr.'s (MEM) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the screen.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Stevens (MEM).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) enters the lane prior to the release of Stevens' (MEM) free throw attempt.
Williams Jr. (MEM) brings his left arm forward toward Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs with Antetokounmpo's right leg as he dribbles in transition.
Lopez (MIL) extends his leg out and makes intentional foot-to-ball contact.
Beasley (MIL) is moving forward when marginal body contact occurs with Williams Jr.'s (MEM) side as Williams Jr. starts his dribble.
Williams Jr. (MEM) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Lillard (MIL) beats Williams Jr. (MEM) to the spot and establishes a legal guarding position prior to Williams Jr. initiating the contact during the driving shot attempt.
Williams (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Lillard (MIL) as simultaneous incidental contact occurs.
Lillard (MIL) dives to the floor in pursuit of the loose ball and makes contact with it prior to incidental body contact occurring with Stevens (MEM).
Williams (MEM) brings his right arm forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Lopez's (MIL) right arm as Lopez makes the pass.
Aldama (MEM) legally contests Lillard's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
